\f1\b0 \cf2 The game of life \'96 I played a lot and loved to play this game!\
I want you to imagine your child walking around bragging about all the money she has acquired or how many kids he has or what type of job he has\'85it\'92s funny and it\'92s cute.\
But imagine for a second that your kid doesn\'92t grow out of it.  He turns 13 and still carry\'92s fake money in his wallet.\
When your daughter is talking to people she can\'92t help but talk about the wonderful white car her and her husband has.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Transition:  I believe the same way you would look at 35 year old man who continues to talk about his game winnings and success, that God looks that way at Christians.  \
