\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92re here today and you would say you\'92re not a Christian I\'92m so glad you\'92re here, I hope to help you understand why so you feel like many Christians are disconnected from what they say they believe and what they do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But if you\'92re here today and you would say that I\'92m a Christian\'85today I want to push you a little bit.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because far too many of us are the 35 year adult who isn\'92t living in reality.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}One reality says this is all there is\'85the other, the Christian reality, says there is something more\'85and at the end of this game we call life\'85all our stuff goes back into the box.  \
