\ls3\ilvl1\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But the practical application is when we fast our ability to withstand temptation grows.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is like a muscle that needs to be developed\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you can deny one of your base needs then your addiction becomes easier to withstand\
